originalText.text:
When we retired in 2019 we wanted to travel, starting with a Viking cruise through Europe.  Finding a travel agent seemed a good idea, and after looking around I came across Gabriella’s Getaways.  I thought, here’s someone who knows Europe.  I gave her a try.

What we’ve experienced over that trip and many others since is  knowledgeable, personable and attentive service. Gabriela is great at laying out our options and following up on our questions with the travel providers (and running further inquiries when she thinks there’s a better answer). She offers tips and suggestions that always help us enhance a trip’s experience.

Gabriela frequently tells us she appreciates our business. I appreciate having a professional partner as I plan our travel schedule.  Kudos to a great travel partner!

originalText.text: I really appreciated Gabriela's planning expertise regarding my family's recent backroad's tour of France. She went the extra mile helping us plan our itinerary, finding us scenic excursions, medieval villages, vineyard visits and prehistoric caves, to name a few. Her meticulous planning assured that we experienced a smooth and very memorable trip. Thank you so much, Gabriela!
